{"tid":1850760,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(有片) 大陸佬直接用刀桶死武漢人 防止病毒傳染","createTime":"2020-01-29T16:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T15:20:07.000Z","uid":222970,"like":233,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"cf592b6ab8dbb24098803c2ef9a44ff230985838","tid":1850760,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:45:46.000Z","msg":"香港人要學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/jrjgh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fjrjgh&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBHyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=6f0b5ac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/jrjgh</a>"},{"pid":"ad529ba46f2a4e4855b6318c031b11a9d39dff7f","tid":1850760,"uid":258731,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東建國 香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廣東建國 香港獨立 港中區隔"},{"pid":"ff7940013698e15bbec51a52b736478d6f19bc5e","tid":1850760,"uid":258731,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"cf592b6ab8dbb24098803c2ef9a44ff230985838","tid":1850760,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:45:46.000Z","msg":"香港人要學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/jrjgh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fjrjgh&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBHyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=6f0b5ac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/jrjgh</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:46:38.000Z","msg":"勇武教科書<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae08bbb2d8e35fa15bfdac467929150e871e465f","tid":1850760,"uid":3747,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:46:39.000Z","msg":"沾血咪重易傳染"},{"pid":"6cf9762a74cdf5d3c8fd3b049cc52dc216233069","tid":1850760,"uid":226955,"like":101,"dislike":1,"score":100,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"死屍亦有傳染效力，咁多人圍住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f45f1a4a03948796371f18545f28b05f39a66cf","tid":1850760,"uid":58209,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"生係武漢人，死係武漢鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},